cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL 

The paper focuses on mobile visual scene understanding, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves the use of recurrent neural networks (RNNs) and deep learning techniques for learning representations (cs.AI, cs.LG). The use of geometric operations and egomotion estimation suggests a focus on robotics and autonomous systems (cs.RO). Finally, the paper also discusses object detection and segmentation, which falls under the subfield of natural language processing (cs.CL) as it involves understanding and labeling objects in a scene.
